direct_answer.text:
Let's think step by step using FOIL. For the first expression, we get:

$$
\begin{align*}
(u+4)(u-1) &= uu - u - 4u + 16 \\
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
(u-3)(u+6) &= uu - 3u - 6u + 18 \\
\end{align*}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
(u+4)(u-1) - (u-3)(u+6) &= uu - u - 4u + 16 - (uu - 3u - 6u + 18) \\
&= uu - 3u - 4u + 18 - 16 \\
&= -7u - 2 \\
\end{align*}
$$

Therefore, the simplified expression is $\boxed{-7u-2}$. The answer is: -7u-2
